short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Open jpg.store listings for Pitches on the Clay Nation map with one click.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension allows users of the map found at https://cnholders.com/map to open the respective listing on jpg.store by clicking on a specific tile on the map.
